<li id="cite_note-FOOTNOTEGirard199432-9"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="René_Girard#cite_ref-FOOTNOTEGirard199432_9-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="René_Girard#cite_ref-FOOTNOTEGirard199432_9-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><a href="René_Girard#CITEREFGirard1994">Girard 1994</a>, p.&#160;32.</span>
