<li><i>To Honor René Girard. Presented on the occasion of his sixtieth birthday by colleagues, students, friends</i> (1986). Stanford French and Italian Studies 34. Saratoga, California: Anma Libri. <link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r951705291"/><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISBN (identifier)">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Special:BookSources/0-915838-03-6" title="Special:BookSources/0-915838-03-6">0-915838-03-6</a>. This volume also contains a bibliography of Girard's writings before 1986.</li></ul>
