<li>Dietmar Regensburger: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.uibk.ac.at/theol/cover/girard/bibliography.html">Bibliography of René Girard</a>. The most detailed bibliography, ending in 2003. <span style="font-size:85%;">Accessed 24 November 2008 </span></li>
<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.morec.com/girard/index.htm">The René Girard Bibliography</a>. A short list of publications. <span style="font-size:85%;">Accessed 24 November 2008 </span></li></ul>
