<ul><li><span class="nowrap"><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Daniel_Hay_du_Chastelet_de_Chambon" title="Daniel Hay du Chastelet de Chambon">Daniel Hay du Chastelet de Chambon</a> (1635)</span></li>
<li><span class="nowrap"><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jacques-B%C3%A9nigne_Bossuet" title="Jacques-Bénigne Bossuet">Jacques-Bénigne Bossuet</a> (1671)</span></li>
